parameters:
The brothel is currently under
renovation due to various circumstances.

Residents: Oh... you have such a cute
reaction. Do you want to do it with me?

Residents: If there's a war, the slums
will become meaningless.

Residents: It's fine to move to the
capital city... well, I do love this
town.

Residents: Are you here to attack us? It
would be best to stop here.
Residents: If there's work, even I...

Resident: I've decided to work
diligently. I feel like I can start over
even now.

Resident: I'm currently working in
delivery service, but it's tougher and
more difficult than I thought...

Residents: Are you also promoting the
brothel? Sorry, but I don't have any
money.

The residents: Logres used to be a quiet
and uneventful town, but it was a warmer
place than it is now.

Residents: ...Did something terrible
happen to you?

Residents: We want to live long, you
know.

Residents: It's dangerous to walk around
dressed like that, young lady...

Residents: ...If you don't have any
business, don't talk to us.

Residents: ...If it's the boy who was in
front of us, he's dead.

The boy who survived when I, who had no
dreams or hopes, died... He had so much
potential...

Resident: If I don't do that, that child
will be pitiful...

Residents: ...Don't walk around dressed
like that.

Residents: Even though both mom and dad
are working, we're struggling to make
ends meet...

Residents: Onee-chan, you're naked! Your
breasts are small!
